<br>
  The level bonus to damage is only applied to the primary hand weapon.  This is important when the class has the ability to double attack with either a one or two-hander.  This incresed damage is more pronounced with haste items.  Since we do not have double attack or 2-handers, the effectiveness of haste on a Bard is less pronounced than on other melee classes. It's nice to have, but other classes need it more than us. <p><font size=2 face="Tempus Sans ITC, Verdana, Helvetica">
